= render 'styleguide/partials/shared'

- components = YAML.load(File.read(File.expand_path('../../../../data/styleguide/forms_stubs.yml', __FILE__)))

.card.styleguide-intro.styleguide-block.copy--body.context--content
  %h1.copy--h1
    Dropdown
  %p
    These are basic selects without javascript but with js enabled they mask the select box whilst still keeping it clickable.

- components['dropdown_components'].each_with_index do |component, i|
  = sg_component("forms/#{component[:styleguide_title].downcase.split(' ').join('_')}", properties: component, count: i, anchor: component[:styleguide_title].downcase.strip.gsub(' ', '-').gsub(/[^\w-]/, ''))
